## Arquivo `.http` para Evolution API

Salve como `.cursor/http/evolution.http` (ou outro caminho) e ajuste variáveis:

```http
# .cursor/http/evolution.http
@baseUrl = https://sua-evolution.com
@apikey = sua-api-key
@instance = meu-numero

### Connection State
GET {{baseUrl}}/instance/connectionState/{{instance}}
apikey: {{apikey}}

### Set Presence
POST {{baseUrl}}/instance/setPresence/{{instance}}
apikey: {{apikey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "presence": "available" }

### Restart
POST {{baseUrl}}/instance/restart/{{instance}}
apikey: {{apikey}}

### Get QR
GET {{baseUrl}}/instance/connect/{{instance}}
apikey: {{apikey}}

### Fetch All Instances
GET {{baseUrl}}/instance/fetchInstances
apikey: {{apikey}}
```
